document.discussion_title: Manuel wins gold in women's 100 free
document.topic_text: American Simone Manuel wins gold in women's 100 freestyle USA TODAY , KING 10:38 Simone Manuel (USA) during the women's 100m freestyle semifinals in the Rio 2016 Summer Games. (Photo: Rob Schumacher, USA TODAY Sports) American Simone Manuel tied with Penny Oleksiak of Canada to win the Olympic gold medal in the 100 free. Copyright 2016 KING
